SCP-[[span class="no"]]████ ███ ██████████ ██ ███ █████████ ██ █ ████ ██████ ██ ████[[/span]], [[span class="no"]]███████[[/span]], [[span class="no"]]█[[/span]].[[span class="no"]]█[[/span]].[[span class="no"]]█[[/span]].[[span class="no"]]█[[/span]]. in [[span class="no"]]████[[/span]]. [[span class="no"]]█████ ██ ██ ███ █████[[/span]] how SCP-[[span class="no"]]████[[/span]]  came into the possession of [[span class="no"]]██[[/span]]. [[span class="no"]]██████[[/span]], [[span class="no"]]██ ███[[/span]] seemingly been aware [[span class="no"]]██ ███ █████████ ██████████[[/span]], [[span class="no"]]██ █████████████ ████ █████ ██ ███ ███████ ██ ███ ████████ ████ ████ ██████████ ██ ██████████ ██ ████████ ███ █████ ████ ██ ███ ██████[[/span]].

[[span class="no"]]██ ████ ████ ██ ██ ███ █████ █████ ████ ██████ ██[[/span]], [[span class="no"]]███ ██ ███ ████ ██████ ██[[/span]] PoI-[[span class="no"]]████[[/span]].

