**Procedure:** The setup found in [[span class="no"]]██[[/span]]. [[span class="no"]]██████[[/span]]'[[span class="no"]]█ ████████[[/span]] was recreated. Several objects were placed nearby, along with [[span class="no"]]███████[[/span]] inside [[span class="no"]]███ ███████[[/span]], with a range of [[span class="no"]]█████ ███ ███████ ██████████[[/span]]. For example, one such [[span class="no"]]████[[/span]] was a [[span class="no"]]███ ██████ ████[[/span]], but another was a [[span class="no"]]████ ██ ███████ ██████[[/span]] in an [[span class="no"]]██████[[/span]] box. SCP-[[span class="no"]]████[[/span]] was [[span class="no"]]█████████[[/span]] under [[span class="no"]]████████ █████████ ██████████ ██████████[[/span]].

